ProjectsArray.Title: WATER REFILLING STATION
ProjectsArray.About: A Water Refilling Station is a facility that provides purified and potable drinking water to customers. Equipped with state-of-the-art filtration systems, these stations ensure the removal of impurities and contaminants from tap water, offering a convenient and reliable source of clean drinking water. Services often include bulk water refills, bottle cleaning and sanitization, and sometimes delivery options, catering to both residential and commercial needs.

ProjectsArray.Title: VULCANIZING SHOP
ProjectsArray.About: A Vulcanizing Shop is a specialized establishment that offers tire repair and maintenance services. Staffed with skilled technicians, these shops utilize vulcanization techniques to mend punctures, tears, and other damages to vehicle tires. Services typically include patching, sealing, and tire inflation, ensuring optimal safety and performance for motorists.
